Date: Sat, 14 Mar 2026 21:21:24 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 11/43] DimmerWindowManager: Add multi-window controls

Add a dedicated DimmerWindowManager to coordinate multi-window controls on top of the pop-up dimmer surface. This separates control layout and state from the main dimmer window logic.
